control_attributes.Control: IA-5 (7) NO EMBEDDED UNENCRYPTED STATIC AUTHENTICATORS
control_attributes.control_description: The organization ensures that unencrypted static authenticators are not embedded in applications or access scripts or stored on function keys.
control_attributes.Control_description: The information system obscures feedback of authentication information during the authentication process to protect the information from possible exploitation/use by unauthorized individuals.
